# My Personal Portfolio Website

This is a simple personal portfolio website built using HTML and hosted using **GitHub Pages**.

## 🚀 Live Demo
[Click here to visit my website](https://harshalv21.github.io/github-pages/)  
(Replace `your-repo-name` with your actual repo name)

---

## 📄 Features
- Personal introduction and bio
- Links to my GitHub and LinkedIn profiles
- Fully responsive (you can enhance it with CSS later)
- Hosted for free using GitHub Pages

---

## 🛠 Tools Used
- **HTML5**
- **GitHub Pages** (for hosting)

---

## 📂 Project Structure
📁 project-folder
├── index.html # Main HTML file
└── README.md # Project documentation


## 🔧 How to Run Locally
1. Clone this repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Harshalv21/your-repo-name.git
Open index.html in your browser.

##🌐 How to Deploy on GitHub Pages

1. Create an index.html file.
2. Push it to a new GitHub repo.
3. Go to repo → Settings → Pages → enable GitHub Pages.
4. Select main branch and root folder.
5. Access live website from the link GitHub gives.

